creator: Outfy
descriptionHtml:
*** Sign-up is unavailable on the Outfy mobile app. Kindly use a desktop or laptop to create your Outfy account and then proceed to use the mobile app seamlessly. ***


Outfy is a powerful social media management tool used by online sellers to create engaging content like product videos, animated gifs, sale promotions, collages and post them on social media automatically.


Outfy posts on TikTok, Instagram, Facebook, Pinterest, YouTube and Twitter. With intelligent AI-assisted scheduling, Outfy plans your posts strategically and avoids sharing sold-out items. Outfy also generates AI-generated captions from product titles and trending, relevant hashtags.
descriptionShort: Share and promote products to all social networks in the fastest & easiest way.
